{"tid":409500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西媒:巴薩獲點球=皇馬2倍！上次被判點是2年前","createTime":"2017-09-22T06:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T14:16:19.000Z","uid":1090,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f64233eb1b7eed8be6fda4955701eb705799a032","tid":409500,"uid":1090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2017-09-22/doc-ifymesii4872432.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.sina.com.cn%2Fg%2Flaliga%2F2017-09-22%2Fdoc-ifymesii4872432.shtml&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNT0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=16e6a376\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2017-09-22/doc-ifymesii4872432.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/20170922/pSHG-fymfcih2389681.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F20170922%2FpSHG-fymfcih2389681.png&h=32c715e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿斯報：巴薩點球數是皇馬翻倍</div><br />\n<br />\n上輪西甲比賽後，伯納烏上下再次表達了對裁判的不滿，而且皇馬認為自己的抱怨是有理有據的。比賽中皇馬又一次遭遇點球被忽略的狀況。哈維&middot;加西亞上半場在禁區內踢倒了馬塞洛，但主裁判並未判罰點球，之後C羅的射門被對方球員手臂擋出，主裁判馬特烏仍然未判罰點球。<br />\n<br />\n　　此外，在皇馬對萊萬特的比賽中，主裁判埃爾南德斯也忽略了特奧應該獲得的一個點球。在皇馬對瓦倫西亞的比賽中，主裁判費爾南德斯又無視帕雷霍禁區內對本澤馬的拉扯。西班牙《阿斯報》指出，皇馬直接被漏掉4個點球，如果這4個點球都能判罰，那皇馬能多得7分，分數剛好和巴薩一樣。<br />\n<br />\n　　《阿斯報》表示，在看到裁判對巴薩和皇馬區別對待後，皇馬球迷可以說是怒火中燒。一個對比數據是在歐洲其它主流聯賽中都找不到的。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">過去兩個賽季76場西甲比賽，加上本賽季的5場西甲，總共81場比賽，巴薩獲得了30個點球，卻只被判罰1個點球，也就是說，點球得失比為+29。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n　　與此同時，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">皇馬獲得了17個點球，差不多只有巴薩的一半，但也被判罰9個點球，得失比為+8，還不到巴薩的1/3。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n　　《阿斯報》指出，本賽季，皇馬還未能獲得1個點球，倒是被判了1個。與此同時，在對埃瓦爾的比賽中，巴薩依靠不存在的點球首開記錄。此外在巴薩對西班牙人的比賽中，巴爾韋德的球隊也依靠梅西一個明顯越位的進球首開記錄。而比賽中首開記錄的進球是非常重要的。<br />\n<br />\n　　巴薩上一次被判罰點球還是在2016年2月14日，已經是將近2年前的事情了。自那之後，巴薩點球得失比為20比0。馬斯切拉諾是巴薩的後防大將，但他上次被判罰點球，居然是5年前的事情了。<br />\n<br />\n　　在紅牌方面，這81輪西甲比賽，巴薩只被出示2張紅牌，而他們的對手被出示21張紅牌。皇馬方面被出示7張紅牌，對手被出示12張。《阿斯報》最後表示，皇馬球迷對裁判憤怒，現在可以理解了吧？（塞爾吉奧）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又話迫害疤狗？</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6cda8580495b6783aae47658daaa4a6105e7b7e","tid":409500,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aefe653e472f39db5c3e2e0153a83faefb28353","tid":409500,"uid":22227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"106bf44035823e7c4b3927218d50b47e6d4f8623","tid":409500,"uid":77948,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"判得多定少都拎得出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係禁區多威脅自然咪多十二碼 <br />\n你不如話巴塞十二碼係水晶宮十9幾倍"},{"pid":"59794d3164e6c3bcf6d9f6e432d0019555355646","tid":409500,"uid":110761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"巴塞個個圍哂係禁區度撚人梗係多十二碼<br />\n賤種蝗淨係遠射同頂波有閪十二碼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105b61035d0a2a72cb166b4c9ccb7eed3f07d711","tid":409500,"uid":101464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:09:17.000Z","msg":"Sor囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多嘔返7分比你地"},{"pid":"0e15ff275ae250ceea6ae07ec7b0a965dbadf1a3","tid":409500,"uid":92656,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"屌奶星我都奇怪疤狗隊廢隊今季憑咩lead住我地無敵銀河艦隊成7分咁多，原來係靠黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a431249dd4b8004d336ba420f1e61c20d88bc9","tid":409500,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅點套餐, 1場20M</blockquote><br />\n仲要拎2.22億去收買球証迫害吾皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1209fa44fcd7e2e1b2296579d13cebe3bca4d30","tid":409500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:10:14.000Z","msg":"賤種想轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n人地場場控球同對手 7:3 8:2 比"},{"pid":"370a7be35124301f43544dd8fa75a2ba3e7cee52","tid":409500,"uid":993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌奶星我都奇怪疤狗隊廢隊今季憑咩lead住我地無敵銀河艦隊成7分咁多，原來係靠黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今季巴狗已經黑左幾次哨，如果唔係一早敗走西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a32add30dd53b5995286915d6d52da875584e0","tid":409500,"uid":9052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"yes 好地地踢波點會有十二碼<br />\n垃圾疤黑撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a30992afa84fa32ea43441403dc1e70fcb0e20","tid":409500,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"唔洗還呀？"},{"pid":"29e3f9c61639fea8ff658f996e9f06d06e44d6e7","tid":409500,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"講到好似有12碼就入硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774eaa7867be4bcef30df7c07a7008c14d308f53","tid":409500,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"自己左腳kick右腳都有12碼啦<br />\n多12碼有幾奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff7fa1adbff161c471d39cc7be19c7a2707e7d5","tid":409500,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"明黑鳩你"},{"pid":"7344bf14ae8564cb241cac4d13824f19c93343c0","tid":409500,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.transfe